      <description>&lt;p&gt;You will be able to find Omega Tokens in the loot or as quest rewards. You will use these as currency to purchase items in the Vanity Shop&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;table-responsive&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;table class=&#34;table table-bordered table-hover table-striped&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;thead&#xA;        &gt;&#xA;          &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;              &lt;th&#xA;                &gt;Item&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;              &lt;th&#xA;                &gt;Details&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;              &lt;th&#xA;                &gt;Cost&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;    &lt;tbody&#xA;      &gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Runic Dye Tub&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This item will allow you to dye your Runebooks. It has 3 charges.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;10&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Omega Dye&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This item will allow you to dye your items. It has 3 charges.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;20&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Soul Pen&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This item will allow you to write your name on your items. It has 3 charges.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;20&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Bear Crystal&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This is a special mount that you will be able to re-summon after it dies by double clicking the item. &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;  &#xA;  &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;35&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Beetle Egg&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This is a special mount that you will be able to re-summon after it dies by double clicking the item.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;35&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Raptalon Scale&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This is a special mount that you will be able to re-summon after it dies by double clicking the item.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;35&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Ki-Rin Lantern&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This is a special mount that you will be able to re-summon after it dies by double clicking the item.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;35&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Wolf Diamond&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This is a special mount that you will be able to re-summon after it dies by double clicking the item.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;35&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Hai Riyo Coin&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;This is a special mount that you will be able to re-summon after it dies by double clicking the item.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;35&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Two-Story Brick House&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;              &gt;Vanity shop exclusive house: See the &lt;a&#xA;  href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/infovault/misc/houses/&#34;&#xA;  &#xA;  &gt;houses&lt;/a&gt; section for details.&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td&#xA;    